tials that would make for a good leadership team at a modern ebike manufacturer, and the good design and engineering decisions that they''ve made with their first commercial product seem to cement that determination.', 'Crowdfunded Ebikes Update: Karmic Koben Approaches $300,000, RadRover Closes with $320,000', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-22 23:46:59', '2015-05-22 23:46:59', '', 34, 'http://overvolted.com/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
