ric-assist model and $2,500 for the conventionally-propelled bicycle.', 'The Denny Ebike Gets A Tentative Launch Date', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-27 17:20:58', '2015-05-28 00:20:58', '', 54, 'http://overvolted.com/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
